longBusinessSummary: Dthera Sciences operates as a digital therapeutic company in neurodegenerative diseases. It is developing DTHR-ALZ, a medical device for the mitigation of the symptoms of agitation and depression associated with Alzheimer's disease. The company is based in San Diego, California.
